  <brief_title>A Study to Examine the Safety and Toleration of PEP005 Topical Gel in Patients With Actinic Keratoses on the Top of the Hand</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center, Open-label Study to Examine the Safety and Toleration of 0.05% PEP005 Topical Gel in Patients With Actinic Keratoses on the Dorsum of the Hand</official_title>
