  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male patients at least 18 years of age.

          -  Post-menopausal female patients

          -  4 to 8 clinically typical, visible and discrete AK lesions within an area on the
             dorsum of one hand.

          -  Written informed consent has been obtained.

          -  Agreement from the patient to allow photographs of the selected AK treatment area to
             be taken and used as part of the study data package.
      </textblock>
